		<title>Economical, custom, modular motors and gearbox drives</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/MotionControlTips/~3/dj-DnLNd3ic/</link>
		<comments>http://www.motioncontroltips.com/economical-custom-modular-motors-gearbox-drives/#respond</comments>
