		<description><![CDATA[<p>Wayne Products now sells aÂ Mini-Skimmer R.S., a belt-type oil skimmer that collects over a quart of oil per hour despite its tiny housing that measures just 3 x 3 x 2.75Â in. Designed as an easy-to-use solution for small machine shops, Mini-Skimmer R.S. skims unwanted tramp oils from coolants, but can rest easily with the flip [&#8230;]</p>
<p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.motioncontroltips.com">Motion Control Tips</a></p>
