		<description><![CDATA[<p>Rotary tables with a high IP rating resistÂ ingress of water and external particles â and the IP65 rating of rotary servo tables from IntelLiDrives assures against ingress of dust and small water jets. IP66 rating assures, in addition to IP65, against ingress of powerful water jets. IP67 rating assuresÂ (in addition to IP66-level protection)Â resistance to water [&#8230;]</p>
